   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The system has minimum clearances requirements from the top <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b> for airflow and to be able to transport the system.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">It is possible to place systems side by side and with the back
to the wall. It is recommended to not have any direct contact.</p>
      <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">Always make sure that there is enough space
for the warm air to dissipate.</note>
